parameters:
Yurika: "You must be feeling it too. The distance between us
is getting closer."

too!!"
\FF[ringo_king]Ringo: "I wanted to convey Master's feelings as well"
\FF[yanagi_king]Yanagi: "Master cherishes you. You don't have to worry"
